Jeffrey Vincent Parise https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeffrey_Vincent_Parise 0 Jeffrey Vincent Parise (born February 8, 1974) is an American actor and artist. Some of his more notable roles include Asmodeus in Supernatural (U.S. TV series), Carlos Rivera and Carlos' twin brother Joe Rivera on the ABC soap opera General Hospital, and Wayne in Anna Biller's horror-thriller film The Love Witch.
